data.description: THIS IS IT! This gorgeous & expansive single level home boasts nearly 1800 sq ft with formal living/room, 4 spacious bedrooms & 2 full baths! Entertainers kitchen features Cherry cabinetry, granite countertops, SS appliances & kitchen island overlooking the spacious great room! Sprawling master bed includes walk-in closet & ensuite bath with double sinks & walk-in shower! Upgrades abound & include vaulted ceilings, wood plank tile throughout, custom farmhouse paint, wainscotting & fully remodeled guest bath with walk-in tile shower! Enjoy your Arizona backyard oasis on a CORNER lot with North/South exposure,  extended patio, pergola with hammock, planter boxes, grass & outdoor kitchen/bar! Located in Alterra, with tot lots, walking & biking paths & close to schools, shopping & Copper Sky!
